<HEADLINE>
<P>
MOTHERS & SONS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Walter Mosley ("Cracking the L.A. Case," by Lynell George, May 22) owes his 
success to his wonderful mother, Ella Mosley, who is retired from the Los 
Angeles Unified School District. However, being very dedicated, she still works 
two to three days a week helping me process applications for children with 
special needs. 
</P>
<P>
 RON DEL BARRIO 
</P>
<P>
 Fontana 
</P>
