<P>
 THE APPLAUSE PERFORMING ARTS GUIDE TO LOS ANGELES & SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA by 
Carey Simon (Applause: $15.95; 479 pp., paperback original). This remarkably 
thorough guide lists literally hundreds of theaters, music and dance 
