<TEXT>
<P>
 *** OutKast, "SOUTHERNPLAYALISTICADDILLACMUZIK," LaFace. This rap duo's debut 
album serves up hip-hop Southern style, with laid-back grooves flavored with 
'70s funk.Their sauntering, hard-core tales of the 'hood bristle with clever 
humor and sharp insights rather than rage. The best cut is the sobering "Git 
Up, Git Out," whose blunt message is: Put down that joint and do something 
productive. 
</P>
<P>
