<TEXT>
<P>
 *** Colin James, "Colin James & the Little Big Band," Virgin. In revisiting 
big-band R&B in the style of Louis Jordan, the Canadian singer-guitarist sounds 
as if he's joy riding in a vintage Caddy.He's clearly enjoying himself, but 
sometimes sounds a bit too respectful, as if worried about nicking the paint. 
Still, his singing is infectious and the band swings like mad. 
</P>
