<P>
 *** Aphex Twin, "Selected Ambient Works Vol. 2," Sire/Warp. You can't really 
dance or even tap your foot to the minimal purr created by Richard James, 
a.k.a. Aphex Twin, who has modified the sound he originally honed in London's 
underground rave parties.There's no real focal point on this two-disc set, but 
instead an all-surrounding sea of synthesized moods. 
</P>
<P>
 New albums are rated on a scale of one star (poor), two stars (fair), three 
stars (good) and four stars (excellent).  
