the toll road, then it seems that a future City Council of Laguna Beach could 
sell the newly acquired Laguna Canyon Parklands back to the developers so that 
we will not just have the toll road running through the canyon -- more housing 
tracts and shopping malls are the ultimate goal of Orange County developers.  
