<P>
 Winning Group F means Belgium would play its round-of-16 match in Orlando, 
where the heat and humidity might be the worst of all the World Cup venues. But 
the players have begun to like the place, despite the weather. 
</P>
<P>
 Maybe they just like the results they've gotten here so far -- 1-0 victories 
over Morocco and Holland. 
</P>
