<HEADLINE>
<P>
KIN VASSY; WORKED WITH FIRST EDITION, OTHER '60S MUSICIANS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Kin Vassy, 50, who performed with Kenny Rogers and the First Edition in the 
1960s and wrote songs for several other musicians, including Bonnie Raitt, Ray 
Charles, Anne Murray and Dionne Warwick as well as the First Edition. He also 
toured with Frank Zappa and the Mothers of Invention. In Los Angeles on 
Thursday of cancer. 
</P>
