WORLD CUP USA 1994; KEEPING THE FAITH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In Cities From Coast to Coast, Fans Have Brought the Color and Pageantry of 
Soccer to America. They Have Sung, Displayed a Huge Swiss Flag and Worn Wigs of 
